trans-unit.source: Provides methods and properties used to perform intelligent, rule-based data point label positioning to resolve overlapping data point label issues.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder og egenskaper som brukes til å utføre intelligent, regelbasert datapunkt etiketten plassering for å løse overlappende datapunkt etiketten problemer.

trans-unit.source: When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.
trans-unit.target: Når smartetiketter er aktivert, flyttes diagrammet overlappende datapunktetiketter, basert på et sett med brukerdefinerte regler.

trans-unit.source: Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.
trans-unit.target: Bildeforklaring linje skal tegnes for å koble etiketten med datapunktet.

trans-unit.source: The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.
trans-unit.target: Visuelle attributter for bildeforklaringslinje linje kontrolleres.

trans-unit.source: These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.
trans-unit.target: Disse visual attributtene omfatter farge, linjestil og linjetykkelse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>egenskapene kontroll diakritiske tegn, for eksempel pilspisser som vises på slutten av linjen bildeforklaringslinje.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A>egenskapen kan settes til noen <xref:System.Drawing.Color>objektet.</xref:System.Drawing.Color> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir farge for bildeforklaringslinje linje, vil du også automatisk angi farge <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>og diakritiske-tegn som er definert av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>egenskapen kontrollerer pikselbredden for bildeforklaringslinje linje.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av denne egenskapen vil også skalere diakritiske tegn <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.
trans-unit.target: Flytting av smartetiketter kontrolleres ved bruk av flere bevegelsesregistrerings-relaterte egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.
trans-unit.target: Disse definerer reglene for flytting for retningen avstanden om datapunktet etiketten er tillatt å forlate tegneområdet.

trans-unit.source: The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.
trans-unit.target: Flytting av standardreglene løser vanligvis de fleste problemer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>definerer en verdi som angir maksimumsavstand i piksler fra dataene peke som datapunktetiketter kan flyttes i overlappende.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>definerer en verdi som angir minimumsavstand i piksler fra dataene peke at datapunktetiketter vil bli flyttet i overlappende.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>

trans-unit.source: When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.
trans-unit.target: Når en peker etiketten må flyttes, blir etiketten flyttes av minst antall piksler som er angitt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>egenskapen angir om etikettene er skjult når overlappende problemer kan løses.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>egenskapen er `true`, og kan ikke tegnes datapunktet i området som er angitt av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>i retninger som tillates av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, vil ikke tegnet datapunktetiketten.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>definerer direction(s) datapunktetiketten kan flyttes.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen godtar en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>verdi eller en-eller bitvis for flere <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>verdier.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>

trans-unit.source: The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.
trans-unit.target: Standard er det-eller bitvis av alle <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>verdier, for å tillate flytte i alle mulige retninger bortsett fra til midten av dataene.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>

trans-unit.source: Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types: - Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.
trans-unit.target: Smartetiketter støttes ikke for følgende diagramtyper: – Coolbar diagrammer: stolpe- og hundre-prosent stablet stolpediagram.

trans-unit.source: - Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.
trans-unit.target: -Figur diagrammer: sektor, hjuldiagrammer Polært og radardiagram diagrammer.

trans-unit.source: - Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.
trans-unit.target: -Område diagrammer: område, område-stolpediagram og liggende for området.

trans-unit.source: - Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.
trans-unit.target: -Stablet arealdiagrammer: stablet området og hundre-prosent stablet arealdiagrammer.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if an algorithm will be applied to prevent data point labels from overlapping.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis en algoritme som brukes for å forhindre at datapunktetiketter overlapper.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref> if overlapping of data point labels will not be prevented.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>Hvis overlappende av datapunktetikettene, ikke vil bli forhindret.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that specifies whether the point labels are allowed to overlap a point marker.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som angir om punktetikettene kan overlappe et merke for datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if data point labels are permitted to overlap point markers.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis datapunkt tillates etiketter overlapper merkene.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref> if data point labels will be prevented from overlapping the point markers.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>Hvis datapunkt vil etiketter bli forhindret overlappende merkene.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that indicates whether overlapped labels that cannot be repositioned will be hidden.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som indikerer om overlappende etiketter som ikke kan flyttes skjules.

trans-unit.source: If the point cannot be drawn within the area specified by the properties <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>, in the directions allowed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, property, and this property is `true`, the data point label will not be drawn.
trans-unit.target: Hvis punktet ikke kan tegnes innenfor området som er angitt av egenskapene <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>, i retninger som tillates av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, egenskapen og denne egenskapen er `true`, vil ikke tegnet datapunktetiketten.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Smart labels only work when the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Angle%2A> property is set to zero.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Smartetiketter fungerer bare når den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Angle%2A>er satt til null.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Angle%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if labels will be hidden if they overlap.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis etiketter skjules hvis de overlapper.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref> if overlapped labels will not be hidden.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>Hvis overlappende etiketter ikke vil være skjult.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir maksimumsavstand i piksler fra dataene peke som datapunktetiketter kan flyttes i overlappende.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir direction(s) der den overlappende <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle"> </xref> objekt kan flyttes.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"></xref> enumeration value or multiple bitwise OR'd <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"> </xref> opplistingsverdien eller flere eller bitvis hadde <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is the bitwise OR of all <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"></xref> values to allow repositioning in all directions except to the center of the data point.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er eller bitvis av alle <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles"> </xref> verdier for å tillate flytte i alle retninger bortsett fra til midten av dataene.
